H3.text: Give a year in the reign of King Stephen.. 1135-1154

A4.text: Stephen was King of England from 22 December 1135 to his death in 1154.

A5.text: King Stephen appointed his son, Eustace IV, Count of Boulogne as co-King on 6 April 1152

A6.text: Eustace died the next year during his father's lifetime
